{"tid":2416571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日日無畏上街 夜夜不同屋匿藏","createTime":"2021-02-21T07:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T07:36:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20958fbc54797c6fbdccbd8a108bf39ac690b84a","tid":2416571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210221/P4JRUFJQ3ZGO3D747CCSROLBIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210221%2FP4JRUFJQ3ZGO3D747CCSROLBIY%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=493c73c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210221%2FP4JRUFJQ3ZGO3D747CCSROLBIY%2F&h=0a44f863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210221/P4JRUFJQ3ZGO3D747CCSROLBIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n日日無畏上街 夜夜不同屋匿藏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TB3zo-VjG0AoEiwO_PSGgRkuLzE=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7YCLOWCQ6JBWHPZ6RNWFDEYNM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTB3zo-VjG0AoEiwO_PSGgRkuLzE%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7YCLOWCQ6JBWHPZ6RNWFDEYNM4.jpg&h=4c014da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曼德勒示威者與警方對峙，群情洶湧。路透社<br />\n<br />\n軍事政變後的緬甸，日和夜對示威者而言是兩個世界：日間成千上萬人結伴無畏上街，以創意標語和妝扮反抗軍政府；但到深夜斷網和宵禁叫天不應、叫地不聞時，恐懼就開始襲來，示威者怕睡到半夜會突然「莫須有」被抓起來，為避搜捕，不少人更晚晚在不同的屋過夜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「精神與肉體的戰鬥」<br />\n<br />\n20歲欣沙順雷伊（Thinzar Shunlei Yi，譯音）是緬甸維權陣營中少見的女性，她坦言長期上街抗爭「是精神也是肉體的戰鬥」；白天去示威已經要想清楚哪一個活動值得冒險，但至少覺得彼此團結強大，「上街是要人民和軍方知道，現有政治制度不行了」，但到晚上就不知道會發生甚麼事，是虛耗意志的「心理戰爭」。<br />\n<br />\n示威者擔心晚上落單時被捕，皆。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n仰光一名不肯透露姓名的年輕示威者說，他也是每天日間上街，夜晚居無定所。「我每天都上街，我們打鼓唱革命歌，為革命打鼓。我們每天抗議，不會停下。」他說：「我不怕中槍，我只怕被捕。」<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網"},{"pid":"a210d3d92efa635b97ca37ca41a1e6e3ae5639bc","tid":2416571,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bb853894d024f89039b4a8c45c11aa0684d685","tid":2416571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}